Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting now, our main mission\Nis to find Itachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and take him into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Akatsuki's goal is to round up the Tailed Beasts.\N It is believed that they already have the Three-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the data obtained by Jiraiya, it's possible they\N have infiltrated the Land of Fire and will target Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi, in particular, is originally\Nfrom the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, he returned to the\N village and attempted to take Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's headed for\Nthe Leaf Village again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as Sasuke\Nwho is after this Itachi Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna meet up\Nwith Sasuke no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just take it\None step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the search plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Using this as the central point,\N we'll search all four directions for five kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If we find nothing, then we'll move the central\N point and spread out five kilometers from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And...we'll keep repeating this strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Five kilometers...\NOur wireless radio will be out of range!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we're separated,\Nit'll be dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules state that all patrols must\Nbe done by two-man cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.83,0:01:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- If we encounter the enemy...!\N- Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Our voices travel even farther\Nthan the wireless radios,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and our noses can instantly\Nsniff out danger, will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pakkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let me explain\Nthe patrol team formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, two ninja hounds will\Nbe assigned to each member.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Two dogs...? Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Get along, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a snappy female\Nas usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm partnering with Shino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... You stink of insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You stink like a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's work together...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In peace and harmony...\NHehehe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if...\N{\i1}I can become friends with dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, you're the Jinchuriki\Nthey're targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case you're attacked,\N you'll be with Yamato and Sensory-Scout Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Big Bark Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's work together, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And being ninja-hound users,\NKiba and I will each have one dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, you will track\NItachi and Sasuke's scents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find either one of them,\N verify their location, then return to this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you, Naruto.\NDon't go running off ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, let's head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:59.82,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(825.938,582.5)}The Hunt\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha, eh?\NI hope we can find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa-su-ke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You too. Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Drat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely healed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Which one are we going for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke or the Nine-Tails...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, which will it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-Wait, D-Deidara Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess underlings don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that Akatsuki...\NWhat's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaku... Kakuta... Kakusa... Kakushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kakuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that Kakuzu's henchman-\Nhis bookkeeper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you anything\Nyou want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just please don't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way... Keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akamaru! Don't lose to\Nthe other ninja hounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the first to detect Sasuke\Nand Itachi's scents!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too slow, Shino!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dawdle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Pochi! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Pochi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me silly nicknames!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wipe that solemn look\Noff your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll scare off the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you chase,\Nthe further they run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a female that keeps\Non pushing, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try pulling away\Nfor a change?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop being so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I want to\Nlet Sasuke know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how I...how everyone feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is waiting for Sasuke\Nto return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Well, if pulling away doesn't work,\Nwhy don't I try sniffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught a whiff of\NSasuke Uchiha's scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell is faint,\Nbut it's steadily getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!\NHe'll be on to us before we find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be cautious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, do you see Sasuke around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.\NThe smell is going farther away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've given it a once-over,\N{\i1}but I don't sense any chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'll go back to Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The other two are probably\N{\i1}not back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it, Tobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding?! That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Which one is it?\NThe Nine-Tails or Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What an opportunity.\NWe're going together, Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto... Hinata...\NYou understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself...\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You found me, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto Yakushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got guts approaching us\Nby yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have a chat\Nwith Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away this time.\NWe're taking you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kabuto! You would know!\NWhere is Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Still can't get over Sasuke, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Sasuke\Nkilled Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly,\NI brought you a present today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That outfit... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Sasuke...\NYou really do look like Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ha!\N- Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Information our organization\Nhas gathered regarding Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yours. You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Orochimaru is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you're trying to negotiate with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope... I don't think it's as easy\Nas negotiating with something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially with the Leaf Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Orochimaru,\NAkatsuki isn't after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a simple gift to Naruto.\NA token of my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Akatsuki is pursuing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gratitude...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After Lord Orochimaru died,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost sense of who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew my parents\Nor my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy found me and from the time I was little,\N I moved around the lands and villages as a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lands and villages didn't\Nmean much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, until I began serving\NLord Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, he's gone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who am I?\NThe agony of not having an identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can understand,\Ncan't you, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd understand\Nanything you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Naruto Uzumaki?\NOr are you the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, you were shunned...\Nregarded with loathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have questioned yourself\Nabout who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you had faith\Nin your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and told yourself that\Nyou were Naruto Uzumaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you boldly overcame\Ntheir views about the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he intend...\Nto do with Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't figure out his intentions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you are sure\Nof your identity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and you found friends\Nwho accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of overcoming\NLord Orochimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I desperately clung to his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really able to understand\Nhow you feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me realize...\Nthat I want to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to surpass Lord Orochimaru whom I absorbed,\N and discover a new stronger self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find my new self...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have given me\Na hint to finding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm grateful...Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochimaru is\Nthe symbol of reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He continues to live on inside me,\Nas an existence that I must overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Took...into your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a small segment of Lord Orochimaru's\N corpse after Sasuke killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,which I transplanted into my own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But, his life-force is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now steadily trying to\Ntake over my body...this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One-third of his body has\N{\i1}already been taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've been fiercely resisting\Nthis takeover!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel this part of me that's trying\Nto overcome Lord Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, give it everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In a jail cell in Leaf Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wood Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm able to fully control\NLord Orochimaru's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight you again, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But you come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First, it'll be Sasuke who\Nbrought down Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do to Sasuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!\NWe brought down Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But looks like he's kinda strong...\Nthis guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine Orochimaru being killed\Nby a brat like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi, look how\Nhe's glaring at us! Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're raring to go, eh Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to apologize to Itachi later.
